'''Afitti''' is an ethnic group in [[North Kurdufan]] in [[Sudan]]. [[Afitti language|Afitti]] is a language of fewer than 10,000 speakers. It belongs to the  [[Nilo-Saharan languages]]. [[Nyimang]] is a related language. Afitti live in the [[Nuba Hills]]. Most members of this group are [[Muslim]]s.

