'''Greg Alyn Carlson''' (born November 2, 1971], [[Washington, District of Columbia]]) is an American criminal who was added to the [[FBI Ten Most Wanted Fugitives]] list on September 27, 2018.<ref name=":0">https://www.fbi.gov/wanted/topten/greg-alyn-carlson</ref> Carlson is an alleged sexual predator involved in multiple armed sexual assaults in [[Los Angeles|Los Angeles, California]] and is wanted on the charges of [[Unlawful Flight to Avoid Prosecution]] and Assault with Intent to Commit Rape<ref name=":0" />. The FBI is currently offering a reward of up to $100,000 for information directly leading to his arrest<ref name=":0" />.

